    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043650/extras/f123c787905d590bb6a2a21f48e4e426.avif?t=1770735791\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043650/extras_big/f123c787905d590bb6a2a21f48e4e426.avif?t=1770735791 width=800 height=281 /></span>You're a group of farmers, you live under a protective dome on a foreign planet. By day you plant your fields, harvest your crops and use them to build wacky defences. Why ? Because by night the local alien species (which aren't too happy about you being here) possess your farm animals and turn them against you. Defend your dome generator and make it through the night ! Survive 10 days and you might be able to get to the next planet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043650/extras/90fd4935f7e54dc1f85cf0b31f0c99a7.avif?t=1770735791\" width=616 height=120 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043650/extras/bafefbaaf368c0a2a5b0397735cf8092.poster.avif?t=1770735791\" width=1170 height=1170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043650/extras/bafefbaaf368c0a2a5b0397735cf8092.webm?t=1770735791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043650/extras/bafefbaaf368c0a2a5b0397735cf8092.mp4?t=1770735791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the location of your fields wisely, then plant your seeds and wait for your plants to grow. Harvest the resources that are fully grown. Always make sure you will have the right resources at the right time in order to build solid defences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043650/extras/3d1b9bfad1a01065a0207045afe6a22d.avif?t=1770735791\" width=616 height=120 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043650/extras/993c767a54839b7d9a490b372bf68eea.poster.avif?t=1770735791\" width=1080 height=1080 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043650/extras/993c767a54839b7d9a490b372bf68eea.webm?t=1770735791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043650/extras/993c767a54839b7d9a490b372bf68eea.mp4?t=1770735791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the resources you have harvested to build, upgrade and heal your wacky defences. From automatic potato cannon to enemy-shredding barrier, use and place them wisely for maximum efficiency. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043650/extras/0ad4ed9d1989cbf901719e8920c10f8e.avif?t=1770735791\" width=616 height=120 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043650/extras/1486e48bf489984ef6287ca839a5a884.poster.avif?t=1770735791\" width=1080 height=1080 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043650/extras/1486e48bf489984ef6287ca839a5a884.webm?t=1770735791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043650/extras/1486e48bf489984ef6287ca839a5a884.mp4?t=1770735791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once night falls, all hell breaks loose. Your farm animals are now possessed by the local alien species, they attack your defences, trying to get to your dome generator in order to disable your only protection against the emptiness of space.</p>",
